324
00:21:08,440 --> 00:21:09,406
Damn it!

325
00:21:14,440 --> 00:21:16,406
I need a little more time!

326
00:21:20,440 --> 00:21:22,373
I'm so close to finishing!

327
00:21:26,373 --> 00:21:27,340
Come on, Rangiku.

328
00:21:32,340 --> 00:21:33,340
You're almost there!

329
00:21:37,340 --> 00:21:38,306
[gasp]

330
00:21:46,840 --> 00:21:47,806
[gasp]

331
00:21:56,306 --> 00:21:56,873
Inexcusable!

332
00:21:59,673 --> 00:22:03,306
